{"tid":1443124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］各位快閃嘅時候都可以做文宣！","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:49:00.000Z","uid":274284,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ecebbc65716b58e133b32a5f578cbbdf34770987","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:43:36.000Z","msg":"雖然小弟係P牌，但懇請連登嘅咁多位聽我一言。<br />\n<br />\n快閃坐地鐵需要時間，除咗休息之外，<span style=\"color: green;\">何不爭取用呢段時間去做更多野去幫成個運動？</span>話唔定呢啲小行動可以增加運動成功嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">坐巴士或者坐地鐵快閃嘅時候，可以試吓：<br />\n1. Airdrop 長輩圖、文宣圖<br />\n2. 派傳單比你身邊嘅普通市民<br />\n等等任何可以宣傳嘅方法</span><br />\n<br />\n文宣嘅內容小弟建議主打721元朗事件，其次打經濟牌，文宣嘅圖可以係telegram channel搵到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">爭取唔同界別、年齡層嘅香港市民支持，將佢地拉入我地嘅陣營，先係令運動持續落去而且導向成功嘅關鍵。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"77398c01dc290507847ce6b7db6e270139a0146e","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"670162602055f9d02164202dfa7c2c4ae4a0f0c6","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0521ac72c86582ee9fea58bf9f9c6a20c98cd4d1","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bff813769d214b38fb5059640a7b4bf7d726733","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:46:11.000Z","msg":"推上去啊！！！！！！"},{"pid":"909001f90bc92730e4b7dfde9d3a614aac2db80b","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f096a6eb5f055f7f618c944b71ad2adcad5dca52","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"如果覺得有用可以幫忙推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /