read/1435712/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n其實藍絲好純真，要佢地支持可能比想像中易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438639/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438639/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非：打破防火牆，用區塊鏈把文宣及資訊倒流中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1435137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1435137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣圖] 話比隔離鄰舍知你嗰區發生緊咩事!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1440766/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1440766/page/1</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e53b9076779627abcedaf112cc521db290df2c28","tid":1443124,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:20:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c7e61ba1347a07ab6768f5eeb5570b61a89b90b","tid":1443124,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"533aacb324ae4ebc98d18c9af0231ab66414b8f2","tid":1443124,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:41:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f206ffcaef4774a1fce365b7f63b9e90bd84f9e","tid":1443124,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"快閃仲有時間文宣<br />\n<br />\n咪癲啦"},{"pid":"5572279e65b85823ce347a89e59b61df9b45ee13","tid":1443124,"uid":274284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f206ffcaef4774a1fce365b7f63b9e90bd84f9e","tid":1443124,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"快閃仲有時間文宣<br />\n<br />\n咪癲啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"down定文宣圖 airdrop諗唔諗得過<br />\n我諗應該唔花太多時間"}]}